title: MetaDickverse
author: MetaDickverse
content: Hello NFT World,MetaDickverse (MDV) is a community driven project identifying and supporting Men's Heath Issues in the Metaverse and beyond. We first launched into the Ethereum blockchain earlier this year on Monday, April 25th 2022. All the MDV NFTs are free mint and minting is on-going on our MDV.ART website. Below you will also find all of our official links for the MetaDickverse project.
